nised%20crime'%20charge%20against%20the%20two%20journalists%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20court%20said%20that%20the%20case%20was%20not%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Borganised%20crime%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20were%20no%20%26quot%3Bmonetary%20transactions%20made%26quot%3B%20so%20the%20charge%20doesn't%20apply%20to%20the%20journalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20court%20maintained%20other%20charges%20under%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%20and%20BNS%20provisions%20related%20to%20creating%20and%20circulating%20false%20information%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20FIR%20prima%20facie%20contained%20well-founded%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Video%20In%20The%20Eye%20Of%20The%20Storm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20erupted%20after%20a%20video%20where%20Ms%20Yadav%20was%20seen%20interviewing%20a%20man%20who%20was%20allegedly%20heard%20using%20derogatory%20remarks%20against%20the%20Congress%20government%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20went%20viral.%20Ms%20Revathy%20allegedly%20posted%20the%20video%20on%20her%20social%20media%20page%20which%20then%20got%20amplified.%20The%20police%20suspect%20the%20video%20has%20been%20shot%20inside%20the%20BRS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20the%20video%20was%20shot%20in%20February%20but%20started%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20on%20March%2010%2C%20allegedly%20to%20coincide%20with%20the%20Budget%20session%20of%20the%20Telangana%20Legislative%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20session%20of%20the%20Telangana%20assembly%20began%20on%20March%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20said%20that%20they%20would%20be%20looking%20into%20the%20funding%20of%20the%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevanth%20Reddy's%20Warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20taken%20a%20strong%20stance%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20warning%20that%20stringent%20action%20would%20be%20taken%2C%20as%20per%20the%20law%2C%20against%20those%20