%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Railways%20allocated%20Rs%208.34%20crore%20to%20IIT%20Madras%20in%20May%202022%20to%20drive%20indigenous%20development%20and%20validation%20of%20Hyperloop%20technology.%C2%A0The%20Union%20Minister%20expressed%20optimism%20about%20India's%20readiness%20to%20adopt%20Hyperloop%20transportation%2C%20citing%20promising%20results%20from%20ongoing%20tests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20entire%20testing%20system%20for%20Hyperloop%20transportation%20has%20been%20developed%20using%20indigenous%20technologies%2C%20and%20he%20congratulated%20all%20the%20young%20innovators%20for%20this%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongratulating%20IIT%20Madras%20on%20its%20cutting-edge%20innovations%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20place%20is%20so%20full%20of%20so%20much%20energy%20that%20I%20cannot%20describe%20it.%20I'm%20so%20happy%20to%20see%20young%2C%20energetic%20engineers%20working%20on%20this%20new%20technology%20and%20doing%20new%20experiments.%20We%20are%20providing%20only%20small%20help.%20I%20think%20that%20this%20will%20really%20lead%20us%20to%20some%20good%20solutions%20for%20the%20country%2C%20for%20our%20people%2C%20for%20our%20start-ups%20and%20for%20the%20world%20of%20technology%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Hyperloop%20Technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIT%20Madras%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20hyperloop%20research%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20years%2C%20significantly%20contributing%20to%20the%20field.%20The%20institute's%20cutting-edge%20facilities%2C%20including%20the%20422-meter-long%20operational%20student-run%20hyperloop%20test%20tube%20and%20track%20at%20Discovery%20Campus%2C%20have%20significantly%20contributed%20to%20advancing%20the%20field.%20IIT%20Madras%20also%20recently%20hosted%20Asia's%20first%20Global%20Hyperloop%20Competition%2C%20supported%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Railways%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuTr%20Hyperloop%2C%20a%20deep-tech%20incubated%20startup%20at%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20is%20set%20to%20launch%20the%20world's%20first%20commercial%20hyperloop%20technology-based%20project%20in%20India%20next%20month.%20This%20historic%20milestone%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20Bharat%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EViksit%20Bharat%202047%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHyperloop%20technology%2C%20conceptualized%20by%20Elon%20Musk%20in%202013%2C%20represents%20the%205th%20mode%20of%20transportation%2C%20enabling%20high-speed%20travel%20in%20a%20near-vacuum%20tube.%20By%20minimizing%20air%20resistance%2C%20the%20capsule%20can%20reach%20speeds%20exceeding%201000%20km%2Fh%2C%20revolutionizing%20the%20future%20of%20transportation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742207940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fg94msb8_hyperloop_625x300_17_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-shares-video-of-indias-hyperloop-tube-soon-to-be-worlds-longest-7942907%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20410-meter-long%20Hyperloop%20test%20tube%20located%20at%20IIT%20Chennai%20is%20already%20the%20longest%20Hyperloop%20test%20facility%20in%20Asia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-shares-video-of-indias-hyperloop-tube-soon-to-be-worlds-longest-7942907%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHamas%20Never%20Stopped%20Digging%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20Hostage's%20Big%20Revelation%20On%20Gaza%20Tunnels%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHamas%20continues%20to%20expand%20its%20vast%20underground%20tunnel%20network%20in%20Gaza%2C%20a%20released%20Israeli%20hostage%20has%20revealed.%20Tal%20Shoham%2C%20who%20was%20held%20captive%20for%20505%20days%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Ffreed-israeli-hostage-speaks-first-time-about-his-505-days-surviving-hamas-hell%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20Hamas%20operatives%20would%20dig%20constantly%2C%20adding%20they%20never%20stopped%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20for%20a%20single%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20network%2C%20named%20the%20%26quot%3BGaza%20metro%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%2C%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20around%20560%20-%20720%20km%20long%2C%20with%20approximately%205%2C700%20separate%20shafts%20leading%20down%20to%20the%20tunnels.%20It%20is%20believed%20to%20stretch%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20with%20tunnels%20connecting%20various%20areas%2C%20including%20military%20bases%2C%20logistics%20centres%2C%20and%20residential%20neighbourhoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnels%20are%20dug%20by%20hand%2C%20using%20simple%20tools%2C%20and%20are%20often%20reinforced%20with%20concrete%20and%20iron.%20The%20network%20is%20designed%20to%20provide%20Hamas%20militants%20with%20safe%20passage%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20move%20undetected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shoham%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%20His%20wife%20and%20young%20children%2C%20aged%20four%20and%20eight%2C%20were%20also%20taken%20that%20day%2C%20though%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20their%20fate%20at%20the%20time.%20Hoping%20to%20protect%20them%2C%20he%20stepped%20outside%20to%20surrender%2C%20only%20to%20be%20surrounded%20by%20around%2040%20armed%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20into%20Gaza%20in%20a%20car%20trunk%2C%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20kneel%20but%20refused%2C%20telling%20his%20captors%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20kill%20me%2C%20kill%20me%2C%20but%20you%20will%20not%20execute%20me%20like%20ISIS.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20then%20paraded%20through%20Gaza's%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2050%20days%2C%20Mr%20Shoham%20didn't%20know%20if%20his%20wife%20and%20children%20were%20alive.%20To%20cope%2C%20he%20imagined%20their%20funeral%2C%20eulogising%20them%20in%20his%20mind.%20%26quot%3BI%20sobbed%20but%20never%20let%20my%20captors%20see%20me%20cry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Fox%20News.%20On%20the%2050th%20day%2C%20he%20received%20a%20letter%20confirming%20their%20survival%20and%20release%2C%20shifting%20his%20focus%20to%20his%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shoham%20was%20held%20in%20isolation%20before%20being%20moved%20in%20with%20other%20hostages.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20and%20three%20others%20were%20transferred%20to%20an%20underground%20tunnel%2C%20where%20he%20would%20remain%20until%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20dire%20conditions%20inside%20the%20tunnel%2C%20surviving%20on%20just%20300%20millilitres%20of%20water%20daily%20-%20for%20both%20drinking%20and%20washing%20-%20and%20plain%20rice.%20The%20lack%20of%20nutrition%20left%20him%20severely%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonths%20into%20captivity%2C%20as%20his%20health%20deteriorated%2C%20a%20doctor%20was%20finally%20brought%20in.%20By%20then%2C%20he%20had%20developed%20a%20severe%20infection%20and%20internal%20bleeding%20in%20his%20legs%2C%20turning%20them%20blue%2C%20yellow%2C%20and%20purple.%20The%20doctor%20provided%20blood%20thinners%20and%20a%20week's%20worth%20of%20vitamin%20supplements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20tasted%20like%20dog%20food%2C%20but%20it%20dramatically%20improved%20our%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shoham%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20supplements%2C%20he%20was%20severely%20underweight%20upon%20his%20release%20from%20Gaza.%20Tal%20Shoham%20and%20another%20hostage%2C%20Omer%20Wenkert%2C%20were%20released%20on%20February%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%2058%20of%20the%20251%20people%20abducted%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20remain%20in%20captivity.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20targeted%20the%20tunnel%20network%2C%20using%20air%20strikes%2C%20artillery%20bombardment%2C%20and%20ground%20forces%20to%20destroy%20the%20tunnels%20and%20disrupt%20Hamas's%20operations.%20Despite%20these%20efforts%2C%20the%20tunnel%20network%20remains%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20functional%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20many%20areas%20repaired.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742207520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fek9qb8sg_tal-shoham_625x300_17_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-ex-israeli-hostage-tal-shohams-big-revelation-on-gaza-underground-tunnels-hamas-never-stopped-digging-7941834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20continues%20to%20expand%20its%20vast%20underground%20tunnel%20network%20in%20Gaza%2C%20a%20released%20Israeli%20hostage%20has%20revealed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-ex-israeli-hostage-tal-shohams-big-revelation-on-gaza-underground-tunnels-hamas-never-stopped-digging-7941834%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Intelligence%20Chief's%20'Islamic%20Caliphate'%20Remark%20On%20Crisis%20In%20Bangladesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20is%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20US%20Intelligence%20chief%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%20told%20NDTV%20World%20today%2C%20speaking%20about%20the%20persecution%20of%20religious%20minorities.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration%20is%20focused%20and%20committed%20to%20defeat%20%26quot%3BIslamist%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20World%2C%20United%20States'%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-and-pm-modi-focused-on-shared-objectives-tulsi-gabbard-to-ndtv-7941747%5C%22%3ETulsi%20Gabbard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20longtime%20unfortunate%20persecution%2C%20killing%2C%20and%20abuse%20of%20religious%20minorities%20like%20Hindus%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Christians%2C%20and%20others%20has%20been%20a%20major%20area%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20US%20government%20and%20President%20Trump%20and%20his%20administration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20new%20Cabinet%20under%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20begun%20talks%20with%20the%20interim%20government%20in%20Bangladesh.%20%26quot%3BThe%20talks%20are%20just%20beginning%20between%20President%20Trump's%20new%20cabinet%20coming%20in%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20but%20this%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20central%20focus%20area%20of%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20Islamic%20extremism%20and%20terrorist%20elements%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20remarks%20she%20spoke%20about%20the%20ideology%20of%20an%20%26quot%3BIslamic%20Caliphate%26quot%3B%20and%20how%20extremist%20elements%20and%20terror%20groups%20globally%20aim%20for%20such%20an%20outcome.%20%26quot%3BThe%20threat%20of%20Islamist%20terrorists%20and%20the%20global%20effort%20of%20different%20terror%20groups%20are%20routed%20in%20the%20same%20ideology%20and%20objective%20-%20which%20is%20to%20rule%20or%20govern%20with%20an%20Islamist%20Caliphate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BThis%20obviously%20affects%20people%20of%20any%20other%20religion%2C%20other%20than%20the%20one%20that%20they%20find%20acceptable%2C%20and%20they%20chose%20to%20carry%20this%20out%20with%20terror%20and%20very%20violent%20ways%20and%20means.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gabbard%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20determined%20to%20identify%20and%20defeat%20such%20an%20ideology%20and%20end%20the%20rise%20of%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Bradical%20Islamic%20terrorism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20remains%20committed%20to%20identifying%20the%20ideology%20that%20drives%20Islamist%20terrorism%2C%20and%20working%20to%20defeat%20this%20ideology%20and%20their%20ability%20exact%20that%20terror%20on%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gabbard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20violence%20and%20religious%20persecution%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20its%20growing%20synergy%20with%20Pakistan's%20notorious%20ISI%20has%20become%20a%20major%20cause%20of%20concern%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Indian%20Army%20chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20ISI%20officials%20in%20Bangladesh%20areas%20close%20to%20India's%20border%20regions%2C%20especially%20the%20Siliguri%20corridor.%20Speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20General%20Dwivedi%20said%20that%20they%20must%20make%20sure%20that%20those%20anti-India%20elements%20must%20not%20be%20able%20to%20use%20that%20soil%20to%20send%20terrorists%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20used%20the%20word%20epicentre%20of%20terrorism%20for%20a%20particular%20country%20(Pakistan).%20Now%20those%20countrymen%2C%20if%20they%20go%20to%20any%20other%20place%20and%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20our%20neighbor%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20am%20concerned%2C%20I%20should%20be%20concerned%20about%20it.%20That%20they%20should%20not%20be%20able%20to%20use%20that%20soil%20to%20send%20terrorists%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20Dwivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20met%20in%20Washington%20in%20February%2C%20the%20US%20President%20had%20said%20that%20he%20will%20let%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20handle%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20been%20working%20on%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Frankly%2C%20I%20have%20been%20reading%20about%20it.%20I%20will%20leave%20Bangladesh%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20Presid