cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsouth-korea-opposition-urges-swift-ruling-on-presidents-fate%2Famp_articleshow%2F119112559.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsouth-korea-opposition-urges-swift-ruling-on-presidents-fate%2Famp_articleshow%2F119112559.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Government%20Bond%20Made%20Investors%20Rich%20By%20Nearly%20200%25%20In%208%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EInvestors%20in%20the%20Sovereign%20Gold%20Bond%20(SGB)%202016-17%20Series%20IV%20and%202019-20%20Series%20IV%20are%20set%20for%20significant%20returns%2C%20with%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20announcing%20the%20final%20redemption%20price.%20The%20investors'%20wealth%20could%20swell%20nearly%203%20times%20on%20redemption%20due%20to%20skyrocketing%20gold%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202016-17%20Series%20IV%20bonds%2C%20issued%20in%20February%202017%20at%20Rs%202%2C943%20per%20gram%2C%20will%20now%20be%20redeemed%20at%20Rs%208%2C624%20per%20gram%2C%20offering%20a%20193%20per%20cent%20return.%20Similarly%2C%20investors%20in%20the%202019-20%20Series%20IV%2C%20issued%20in%20September%202019%20at%20the%20same%20price%2C%20can%20prematurely%20redeem%20the%20bonds%20at%20Rs%208%2C634%20per%20gram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20redemption%20for%20both%20series%20is%20scheduled%20for%20March%2017%20based%20on%20the%20average%20closing%20price%20of%20999%20purity%20gold%20between%20March%2010%20and%20March%2013%2C%20this%20year%2C%20as%20published%20by%20the%20India%20Bullion%20and%20Jewellers%20Association%20(IBJA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Redemption%20Price%20Is%20Calculated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20redemption%20price%20for%20early%20exit%20is%20based%20on%20the%20average%20gold%20price%20(999%20purity)%20for%20the%20three%20business%20days%20before%20the%20redemption%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20bond%20series%2C%20IBJA%20has%20calculated%20the%20price%20using%20gold%20rates%20from%20March%2011%2C%2012%2C%20and%2013%2C%202025.%20Sovereign%20Gold%20Bonds%20(SGBs)%20have%20an%20eight-year%20maturity%2C%20but%20investors%20can%20exit%20after%20five%20years%2C%20only%20on%20interest%20payment%20dates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20SGB%20Series%20IV%202019-20%2C%20the%20earliest%20redemption%20date%20is%20March%2017%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERedemption%20Process%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20redeem%20the%20bonds%20prematurely%2C%20investors%20must%20submit%20a%20request%2030%20days%20before%20the%20interest%20payment%20date%20at%20their%20designated%20bank%2C%20SHCIL%20office%2C%20post%20office%2C%20or%20agent.%20The%20request%20must%20be%20made%20at%20least%20one%20day%20before%20March%2017%2C%20to%20be%20processed%20successfully.%20Once%20approved%2C%20the%20proceeds%20will%20be%20credited%20directly%20to%20the%20investor's%20bank%20account%20linked%20to%20the%20SGB%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBenefits%20Of%20Premature%20Redemption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremature%20redemption%20gives%20investors%20early%20access%20to%20their%20money%20instead%20of%20waiting%20for%20the%20full%20maturity%20period.%20It%20also%20allows%20them%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20higher%20gold%20prices%20while%20keeping%20their%20investment%20safe.%20Since%20gold%20prices%20have%20risen%20significantly%2C%20exiting%20now%20could%20be%20a%20smart%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBenefits%20Of%20Holding%20SGBs%20Until%20Maturity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20highlight%20the%20advantages%20of%20holding%20SGBs%20for%20the%20full%20tenure%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETax-Free%20Gains%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%20capital%20gains%20tax%20if%20held%20till%20maturity.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuaranteed%20Interest%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202.5%20per%20cent%20annual%20interest%20ensures%20a%20st